text: Landenbeckerbruch is a locality in the municipality Schmallenberg in the district Hochsauerlandkreis in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. The hamlet has 6 inhabitantsSchmallenberg.de: Inhabitants and lies in the west of the municipality of Schmallenberg at a height of around 430 m. Landenbeckerbruch borders on the villages of Keppel, Arpe, Niederberndorf and Niederlandenbeck. ==References== Category:Villages in North Rhine-Westphalia Category:Schmallenberg
